# YourDollarsOnline E-commerce Platform

## Setup Instructions

1. Install dependencies:
   npm install

2. Set up environment variables:
   Create .env.local with:
   REDIS_URL=your_redis_url
   REDIS_TOKEN=your_redis_token
   JWT_SECRET=your_jwt_secret

3. Initialize database:
   Visit /api/init to create admin user

4. Seed sample data:
   Visit /api/seed to add sample products

5. Start development server:
   npm run dev

## Features

- Dynamic fluid navbar that updates based on product categories
- Real-time search with dropdown suggestions
- Admin dashboard with product management
- SEO-optimized product pages
- Modern responsive design
- Redis database integration
- PayPal payment integration ready

## Admin Access

Default admin credentials:
- Username: admin
- Password: admin123

## API Endpoints

- GET /api/categories - Get all product categories
- GET /api/search?q=query - Search products
- GET /api/products - Get all products
- POST /api/products - Create new product (admin only)
- GET /api/init - Initialize database
- GET /api/seed - Seed sample data

## File Structure

- src/app - Next.js pages and API routes
- src/components - React components
- src/lib - Utility functions
- public - Static assets

## Deployment

Ready for Railway deployment with proper environment variables.
